      "contents": "<div class=\"markitup-box\">\n\t\t\t是黄种人的暴力基因导致<br/>\n[url=https://www.google.com/url?sa=t&amp;source=web&amp;rct=j&amp;opi=89978449&amp;url=https://m.163.com/dy/article/ICBLTLJD055619C1.html%3Fspss%3Dadap_pc&amp;ved=2ahUKEwjauY-hgNiBAxWklIkEHUd3C-8QFnoECAsQAQ&amp;usg=AOvVaw0z-zs6fcUH2R8Pii1PHfVS][/url]东亚黄种人有超高的“战士基因”突变，这个突变被称为暴力变态狂突变或者战士突变\t\t</div>",
